&lt;a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/masayun/4720545977/" title="液晶保護シート装着後画面 by masayukig, on Flickr"&gt;&lt;img alt="液晶保護シート装着後画面" loading="lazy" src="http://farm2.static.flickr.com/1373/4720545977_8ef304f750.jpg"&gt;
